about.summary: Routines for generating and parsing KiCAD files

name: pykicad
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pykicad" %}
{% set version = "0.1.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ded058f3af116845d8a0495f3a8ff4b6a7e707e534c5b71ee61b37fb23553923

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3
    - pyparsing

test:
  imports:
    - pykicad

about:
  home: https://github.com/dvc94ch/pykicad
  license: ISC
  license_family: Other
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Routines for generating and parsing KiCAD files'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hmaarrfk
